1
00:00:02,830 --> 00:00:04,830
I can't believe you agreed.

2
00:00:07,880 --> 00:00:09,540
The media was there, after all.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:10,920
You never know who might be eavesdropping.

4
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:12,330
Who knows.

5
00:00:12,920 --> 00:00:14,290
You didn't say 'forgive,'

6
00:00:15,130 --> 00:00:16,710
you said 'approve.'

7
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:19,460
My daughter
is her own person.

8
00:00:20,250 --> 00:00:21,630
It's not a father's place

9
00:00:21,630 --> 00:00:24,210
to decide whether to forgive
or not.

10
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:27,080
No matter how many times
you try to stop me,

11
00:00:27,920 --> 00:00:29,420
I will protect her.

12
00:00:29,540 --> 00:00:30,540
At any cost.

13
00:00:31,330 --> 00:00:33,130
I love Reika.

14
00:00:34,040 --> 00:00:35,540
Seeing her resolve,

15
00:00:36,290 --> 00:00:37,960
I simply

16
00:00:38,630 --> 00:00:39,960
wanted to give them my blessing.

17
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:41,130
That's all.

18
00:00:43,170 --> 00:00:44,880
So you're not the big bad dad anymore.

19
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:48,880
You thought I was the big bad dad, huh?

20
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:50,960
Ah, I hope I can soon

21
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,420
be friends with her again.

22
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:55,670
Hey, don't you dare
ignore me.

23
00:01:11,210 --> 00:01:12,670
We can finally

24
00:01:12,670 --> 00:01:14,330
eat together
out in the open.

25
00:01:14,500 --> 00:01:15,500
Yeah.

26
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,830
Don't get any funny ideas.

27
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,290
I won't.

28
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,040
Sami.

29
00:01:24,630 --> 00:01:27,040
There's something I've been meaning

30
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,460
to tell you.

31
00:01:32,210 --> 00:01:33,210
I'm sorry.

32
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:37,080
I did so many
awful things to you.

33
00:01:37,750 --> 00:01:39,500
I knew I had to
apologize to you.

34
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,420
Even though you were always

35
00:01:41,420 --> 00:01:42,920
the one protecting me.

36
00:01:45,670 --> 00:01:46,750
It's okay.

37
00:01:52,250 --> 00:01:54,750
I told you to stop.

38
00:01:54,750 --> 00:01:55,710
Because you're kind

39
00:01:55,750 --> 00:01:57,420
and cool.

40
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,130
Well then.

41
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:02,880
To make it up to me,
what should I have you do?

42
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,130
I'll do anything.

43
00:02:05,670 --> 00:02:06,670
In that case,

44
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:11,250
you can do the cleaning and laundry
for the rest of your life.

45
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:12,880
The rest of my life?

46
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:15,080
Wait, are you saying
you want to live together?

47
00:02:15,130 --> 00:02:16,580
I'm so happy!
